    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering with this 1997 Toyota Supra Turbo. Under the hood lies the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring a sequential twin-turbocharger system that delivers linear power throughout the rev range. This example is equipped with the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for superior torque management. The factory double-wishbone suspension and four-piston brake calipers provide exceptional lateral grip and stopping power. Mechanically sound with consistent boost pressure and precise shift gates, this A80 chassis is a well-maintained driver\u2019s car perfect for the purist.",
      "price": 38500.0,
