    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-cared-for example of a modern classic, striking an excellent balance between aesthetic appeal and mechanical reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of respectful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, and the original floor mats have been preserved under all-weather protectors. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is tidy, showing no signs of leaks or neglect. The car has a documented service history, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection that confirmed the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth, quiet ride that speaks to its consistent upkeep. This is a dependable, honest car ready for immediate daily use.",
